 Pre-Publish Checklist                                                 
                                                                        
  Metadata (package.json)                                               
  - author field uses your Raycast account username                     
  - license set to MIT                                                  
  - Latest Raycast API version                                          
  - package-lock.json included (they use npm for CI)                    
                                                                        
  Build Verification                                                    
  - Run npm run build - must complete without errors                    
  - Run npm run lint - check code quality                               
  - Test the built extension actually works in Raycast                  
                                                                        
  Required Assets                                                       
                                                                        
  Icon                                                                  
  - 512x512 PNG                                                         
  - Works in both light and dark themes                                 
  - No default Raycast icons allowed                                    
  - Use https://icon.ray.so to generate one                             
                                                                        
  Screenshots                                                           
  - 2000x1250 PNG (16:10 ratio)                                         
  - 3-6 screenshots recommended                                         
  - Consistent background, no sensitive data                            
                                                                        
  Naming Guidelines                                                     
                                                                        
  - Use Title Case (Apple style)                                        
  - Prefer nouns over verbs ("Emoji Search" not "Search Emoji")         
  - Be specific about what it does                                      
  - Commands: verb + noun structure                                     
                                                                        
  Code Quality                                                          
                                                                        
  - Use the Preferences API (not custom config commands)                
  - Handle empty states with List.EmptyView/Grid.EmptyView              
  - Use Navigation API for screen transitions                           
  - No external analytics                                               
  - US English spelling                                                 
                                                                        
  Documentation                                                         
                                                                        
  - Add a README if setup/configuration is required                     
  - Include CHANGELOG.md for version history                            
                                                                        
  Publishing Process                                                    
                                                                        
  1. Run npm run publish                                                
  2. Authenticates via GitHub and opens a PR to raycast/extensions      
  3. Raycast team reviews and may request changes                       
  4. Once merged, it goes live in the Store                             
                                                                        
  Any specific area you want me to look at in your extension?   


